what they were talking about.

280
00:17:30.833 --> 00:17:33.583
Really thought that
you could help me.

281
00:17:37.916 --> 00:17:40.625
-What's your name?
-Gunner Boone.

282
00:17:40.625 --> 00:17:43.875
Gunner Boone. you swear
this isn't a prank?

283
00:17:43.875 --> 00:17:45.583
I cross my heart.

284
00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:08.208
